title: Tsuyokute Kakkoii Joshi wa Suki desu ka?
original_name: 強くてカッコイイ女子は好きですか?
sinopse:
In order to become a strong and cool girl, high school girl Mie Tsukasa joins a professional wrestling organization.

Follow her intensive training every day together with her trainer, with the aim of becoming a pro-wrestler.

(Source: MU)
